  "transformation": "Parse OpenDSS lines, the pinned shared line-code impedance matrices, phase connections, loads, transformers, regulator controls, capacitors, and switch states. Aggregate public load records by base bus while preserving record-level phase connections. Form contingencies only by deterministic N-1 opening of listed in-service lines and transformers. Published line codes have no ampacity field, so no line rating is inferred."
